    "result": {"data":{"strapiPost":{"strapiId":3355,"title":"Pardon the Interruption","topic":"Economy","slug":"pardon-the-interruption","coverImage":{"publicURL":"/static/190b7351e0cf33e3e12ee2eb8e4e0fd4/b75de958db225871df89f3d5d5559317.jpeg"},"photoCredit":"NWA Daily","date":"2021-07-24","content":"<p>A decade of growth in NWA's <a href=\"https://talkbusiness.net/2021/07/arkansas-tourism-ticker-recovery-comes-into-view-hotels-still-lag/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">tourism industry</a> was interrupted in 2020 by the pandemic. However, the tourism industry is on its way back to regular <a href=\"https://talkbusiness.net/2021/07/arkansas-tourism-ticker-recovery-comes-into-view-hotels-still-lag/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">growth</a>.</p><ul><li><strong>Road to recovery: </strong>Across the state, Jan-Apr tourism tax revenue is up <a href=\"https://talkbusiness.net/2021/07/arkansas-tourism-ticker-recovery-comes-into-view-hotels-still-lag/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">42.5%</a> from last year and 4.1% from <a href=\"https://talkbusiness.net/2021/07/arkansas-tourism-ticker-recovery-comes-into-view-hotels-still-lag/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">pre-pandemic records</a>. </li><li><strong>Local report: </strong>Rogers and Springdale are still facing <a href=\"https://talkbusiness.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/TourismTicker_Jan-April2021.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">some challenges</a>, but Bentonville and Fayetteville both saw double-digit <a href=\"https://talkbusiness.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/TourismTicker_Jan-April2021.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">percentage increases</a> in tourism tax numbers. Tourism jobs in NWA have also increased with a <a href=\"https://talkbusiness.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/TourismTicker_Jan-April2021.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5.3%</a> boost from a year ago.</li></ul><p>You can read through the full <a href=\"https://talkbusiness.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/TourismTicker_Jan-April2021.pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Arkansas Tourism Ticker</a> to find out more about the road ahead.</p><p><em>Story courtesy of Talk Business &amp; Politics</em></p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"pardon-the-interruption"}},
